	TRANSPORT
	cells 10
	lengths 0.5e-3
	timest 1 day 5
	shifts 2 0
	multi_d true 0.5e-9 0.3 1e-6 1.0 false
	porosities 4*0.001
	boundary_conditions constant closed
	punch_frequency 1
	USER_GRAPH 
WARNING: Cell-lengths were read for 1 cells. Last value is used till cell 10.
WARNING: No dispersivities were read; disp = 0 assumed.
WARNING: Porosities were read for 4 cells. Last value is used till cell 12.
	-axis_titles "distance / mm" "mol" pH
	-conn false
	-headings x Litha H-Cer Cc pH..+..1day
	-plot_concentration_vs dist
	-axis_scale x_axis 0 4
	10 graph_x dist * 1e3
	12 if cell_no = 4 then li = 0e-3 else li = 0
	20 graph_y equi("Litharge") - li, equi("Hydrocerussite"), equi("Calcite")
	30 graph_sy -la("H+")
	END
